        A -->|Disconnect| C[Power BI: DAX Logic]
        B -.-|Mismatch| C
    end

    subgraph SOLUTION ["‚úÖ The Solution: Open Governance Schema"]
        D[("JSON Schema (OGS)
        Single Source of Truth")] 
        
